OL,3,CGlimmer of hope for triple hernia
OL,4,Cpatient after 4-year fight for
OL,5,Coperation on the NHS
OL,7,FITV Granada Reports journalist Mel
OL,8,FBarham spoke to Winston Baldwin.
OL,10,FA former dairy farmer from Crewe, who
OL,11,Fhas been fighting for an operation on
OL,12,Fthe NHS for the last four years, has
OL,13,Ffinally been given a glimmer of hope.
OL,15,FWinston Baldwin, 74, has been living
OL,16,Fwith a triple hernia since 2019.
OL,18,FHis treatment was delayed during
OL,19,Fcovid, and last year he was told it
OL,20,Fwas so advanced that the hernia was
OL,21,Fnow inoperable.
